data.description: Florida living at its best! Beautifully presented waterfront home with views that wrap around the home and the gorgeous lot upon which it sits. The home has been remodeled to take advantage of the location with water views from almost every aspect. Great curb appeal, open floor plan, new windows in 2007 and new roof in 2006! Lots of extras including built in seating in den area, screened porch, open patio area and floating dock for your enjoyment. You must put this on your list to see. Buy a piece of paradise now while such fabulous property is still affordable!
